item.title: [ENTESB-4431] [Patch mechanism] Unable to upgrade ssh container with build 073 (container doesn't start)
item.description:
There is problem with upgrading ssh container created on GA version to 073. All patch commands are executed without problem but then I am unable to start container. Calling container-start command doesn't work and container never starts again. Also there are lot of these exceptions, which seems to be root of this problem:
